<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和八戒迅速飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们飞出美罗城，飞过高山，落在一片草地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个，悟空。” 八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你来找我，我真怕自己一个人被困在这个世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还好找到了你，八戒。” 悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要睡一会儿。” 八戒躺在地上说，“然后我们再去找师父吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没觉得哪里奇怪吗？” 悟空看了看四周说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没什么奇怪的呀。” 八戒说着闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些山和我们之前走过的山很像。” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是有一点不一样——这里没有妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道？” 八戒哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能看得很远，也能感觉到妖怪的存在。” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我发现，来到这个世界以后，我没感觉到任何妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许我们可以在这里住一段时间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不喜欢这个世界。” 八戒皱了皱眉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们把我关进监狱，就因为我吃了一些食物？哼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拍着下巴：“我们占领这个地方怎么样？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样就没人把你关进监狱，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且我们也可以休息一下，不用和妖怪打架。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “好主意！但是，这里有一个非常强大的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空扬了扬眉：“你是说火箭女孩儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你见过她？” 八戒问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空点了点头：“她很强大，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她不在这里——我把她送去了我们的世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做得好！” 八戒笑着说，“那我们就占领这里吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的人都要听我们的！我要吃光他们所有的食物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“占领这个王国的话，还需要一个军队。” 悟空认真想着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得回一趟花果山。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克从沙发上跳下来，打转、踢腿、挥拳，“我是猴子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉笑着哼了一声：“看我看我——我是大猪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打了一个大大的嗝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和玛拉哈哈大笑的时候，特勒尔偷偷走出房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出手机，给罗西打电话，但是罗西还是不接电话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西到底在哪儿？” 特勒尔叹了一口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她为什么不接我的电话？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开门，妖怪！” 罗西大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用拳打门，用脚踢门，大骂着妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，黑雨大王打开了门：“你怎么还在这里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上放了唐僧！” 罗西跺着脚大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！” 黑雨大王瞪着罗西，“你这个粗鲁的人！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我正在休息，你却在这里大喊大叫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咻！罗西的眼睛发出激光，打在黑雨大王的脸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！” 黑雨大王打出一拳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳到旁边：“哈！你没打中……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼！强风暴雨再次把罗西吹跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她翻滚着从山坡上掉下来，最后掉进了一个灌木丛里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山上的洞门砰的一声关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！” 罗西正要飞回山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然出现了一个老奶奶：“别再上去了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>